duties_responsibilities.duty: Greet customers, run the register, cashier, make purchase suggestions, and work with the food program.
Maintain high standards for store appearance and provide fast and friendly service to customers.
Interact with many customers daily while working with a fun, energetic team to accomplish daily tasks around the store.
Perform at a quick pace, work as part of a team, and come up with ideas to solve problems.

education_certification.credential: High School diploma or GED preferred.
